<P>
 Lilly, Biotech Firm in Venture: Indianapolis-based Eli Lilly & Co. said it is 
teaming with Somatogen Inc. to make artificial hemoglobin that could be used as 
a blood substitute in emergencies.Boulder, Colo.-based Somatogen developed the 
product and is testing it with patients. The partnership will join a handful of 
